- **Spacetime as a Fabric**: Imagine spacetime as a stretchy fabric. Massive objects like stars warp it, creating "gravity wells" (Term intuitive="Space-Occupier" jargon="Fermion" definition="Particles that occupy space and resist being compressed" />).  
